{"tid":982450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★none buy iphone！蘋果2018年更換約1100萬塊iPhone電池，是過往數量的11倍","createTime":"2019-01-15T06:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T09:00:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b708a7ba156f29e0b54ea3a3bb862093d42e3c5d","tid":982450,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"IT之家1月15日消息 在蘋果公司對其2019年第一季度收益進行修訂後，蒂姆庫克舉行了全體會議，與蘋果員工討論結果。雖然會議的大部分細節尚未洩露，但是據外媒報導，爆料人John Gruber在今天發布了一個有趣的消息。<br />\n<br />\n在全體會議期間，蒂姆庫克表示，在29美元的更換計劃的期間，蘋果公司更換了1100萬塊iPhone電池。庫克在會議期間表示，在正常的一年中，蘋果會計劃更換大約100萬到200萬個電池<br />\n<br />\n29美元的替代計劃活動了將近一年。這意味著在2018年裡，蘋果更換了一年中通常要更換的電池數量的11倍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/405/656.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F405%2F656.htm&d=IaM7PEbqaTm0p1rdo6owMW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1b40f34a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/405/656.htm</a>"},{"pid":"010f8db09c8caeca96bf4b173c4ad7f62feacbaa","tid":982450,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T07:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e42daf8225d1e1e9ae72e0720b3a94d085aa45e","tid":982450,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"換粒電 又一條好漢"},{"pid":"3406b8eee4d76fa04cbabee3b753e66659681f00","tid":982450,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e42daf8225d1e1e9ae72e0720b3a94d085aa45e","tid":982450,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"換粒電 又一條好漢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d293baafdba59e2d87d52b7a51584b09bad41fbf","tid":982450,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"永續換電法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr